Cell["\<\
The Private option DividedPeriodicEventList signals the construction of a \
subdivided list of periodic events, used for feeding the COMPUTE algorithm. \
This option is used as a flag so that the construction of a subdivided event \
list is performed outside the ensemble average.\
\>", "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
