3.6.1 sidestep diagonalization if a NDiagonalize error is detected (often \
needed for Lindbladians)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.837949615969057*^9, 3.837949649829791*^9}, {
  3.837950212930787*^9, 3.837950214355713*^9}, {3.837950323278903*^9, 
